videos.headline: Georgia Tech jumps in front on 33-yard TD run
videos.description: QB TaQuon Marshall keeps it himself on the option play and explodes through a hole, giving the Yellow Jackets a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech doubles lead on Marshall's 2nd TD run
videos.description: TaQuon Marshall gets behind his blockers and crosses the goal line for a 1-yard touchdown run, making it 14-0 Yellow Jackets.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech registers 3rd rushing TD of 1st quarter
videos.description: RB Jordan Mason finds a seam and gets to the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown run to make it 21-0 Yellow Jackets.

videos.headline: Louisville gets on board with 29-yard TD pass
videos.description: Jawon Pass drops a dime to WR Tutu Atwell, who brings it in and cuts Georgia Tech's lead to 21-7.

videos.headline: Louisville gets back in it with 5-yard TD run
videos.description: RB Trey Smith makes a nice cut and punches it into the end zone to narrow Georgia Tech's lead to 24-14.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech responds with TD before half
videos.description: RB Qua Searcy takes the pitch and glides into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown run, making it 31-14 Yellow Jackets.

videos.headline: Searcy blows it open for Georgia Tech with 2nd TD of game
videos.description: RB Qua Searcy lays out and breaks the plane for a 1-yard touchdown run to make it 38-17 Yellow Jackets.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech QB rips off 65-yard run to set up his own rush TD
videos.description: Backup QB Tobias Oliver breaks free for 65 yards up the sideline before scoring on a 5-yard quarterback keeper.
